<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Porhhlawt ruam-kainak in ka rak um, Ka Bawipa thihnak zei rel loin, A
 thihnak kha zei ti hngalh loin, Kal-va-ry ah.

[C1]
   Amah velngeih, zaangfahnak thawngin, Ngaih-thiamnak man loin ka hmuh
   cang, Ka thlarau nih thilrit a thumh cang, Kal-va-ry ah.

[V2]
 Pathian bia in ka sualnak ka hngalh, A bia ka al ca'h ka tha a ther, A
 sual ka thlarau a thian hlantiang, Kal-va-ry ah.

[C2]
   Amah velngeih, zaangfahnak thawngin, Ngaih-thiamnak man loin ka hmuh
   cang, Ka thlarau nih thilrit a thumh cang, Kal-va-ry ah.

[V3]
 Atu ka zeizong Jesuh ka pek, Ka lung a ka lawmhter tu Bawipa, Ka
 thlarau nih lawmhnak hla a sak, Kal-va-ry ah.

[C3]
   Amah velngeih, zaangfahnak thawngin, Ngaih-thiamnak man loin ka hmuh
   cang, Ka thlarau nih thilrit a thumh cang, Kal-va-ry ah.

[V4]
 Maw dawtnak thiang bik, Khamhnak sertu, Velngeihnak mi cung a
 tluntertu, Pathian nih pehtlaihnak hlei a donh, Kal-va-ry ah.

[C4]
   Amah velngeih, zaangfahnak thawngin, Ngaih-thiamnak man loin ka hmuh
   cang, Ka thlarau nih thilrit a thumh cang, Kal-va-ry ah.</lyrics>
<title>KALVARY AH CH264</title>
<hymn_number>264</hymn_number>
</song>